  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[On Play][When Digivolving] Place 1 [Raijinmon], 1 [Fujinmon],
    and 1 [Suijinmon] from your trash under this Digimon in any order as its bottom
    digivolution cards. Gain 1 memory for each card placed.[When Attacking] If the
    level 6 cards in this Digimon's digivolution cards have 3 or more colors among
    them, this Digimon gets +3000 DP until the end of your opponent's turn. If they
    have 4 or more colors, \uFF1CDe-Digivolve 1\uFF1E 1 of your opponent's Digimon."
